title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Wooden toys for children that last.” [From the headline of a Do It Yourself column in The Miami Herald, May 13, 1984, p. 2H. Submitted by Mrs. Murray M. Kassel, Ft. Lauderdale, Florida.].
